{"tid":89120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陽具有如小象鼻　生活辛酸誰人知","createTime":"2017-01-21T06:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T12:58:08.000Z","uid":22736,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17fdaa00718cffeaade642210cd03c66ea56a45f","tid":89120,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/latest/230220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Fbreakingnews%2Flatest%2F230220&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3dbeb7eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/latest/230220</a><br />\n墨西哥男子卡布瑞拉(Roberto Esquivel Cabrera)擁有48.2公分陽具，但他生活一點也不快樂，靠著政府補助過活，近日透露想到美國當男優念頭。<br />\n <br />\n英國《鏡報》報導，異於常人的陽具為卡布瑞拉帶來名利，卻無法登入《金氏世界紀錄》。醫生懷疑他過度沉溺於陰莖長度，而且是後天加工把陰莖拉長的。醫生認為他自青少年時期就在陰莖上綁繩帶，用重量慢慢拉長陰莖。<br />\n <br />\n也因為陽具過長，卡布瑞拉有健康與衛生問題。卡布瑞拉的包皮過長，尿道時常發炎感染，平常都要把陰莖包在繃帶與絲襪內，才不會因為走路摩擦疼痛。當然夜晚時他的陰莖也有自己的小枕頭，避免陰莖被壓傷。<br />\n <br />\n此外，卡布瑞拉的陽具只有排尿功能，沒有女性願意和他做愛，過去一名女性見到他的陽具當場逃跑，另一名女子則因疼痛喊停。<br />\n <br />\n卡布瑞拉希望未來能到美國就業，「美國有很多女生，在那一定能找到適合的人，我希望餘生能在那度過」，「我想當A片男優，我一定可以在那賺很多錢」。（余浚安／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n（本篇圖文由《蘋果日報》提供）<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZkNeEus6aNCBhAyd6j7oHoJ1kS4Y5pJQAdZqoVhKcXVT?filename=pcq73f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpcq73f8.jpg&h=48c3abd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSnziHRpEVQiyWFPDvzANscmibfqqEHaeF5vnPdK7aaf6?filename=tZ0w313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZ0w313.jpg&h=e7541191&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e970325176f1efc8493844d857d791b80adc9b9","tid":89120,"uid":45597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"同連登仔有得fight<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7a56cd84cf400555816dcb8cbb2aada1ba623b","tid":89120,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite